.DS_Store

# Notes for the AirBuddy developer — not part of the extension
FEEDBACK.md
# docs/superpowers/ (local planning artifacts) is ignored; docs/solutions/ (ce-compound knowledge
# base) is tracked and meant to be shared. A bare `/docs` exclude stops git from descending into the
# directory at all, so a nested `!docs/solutions/` rule can't resurrect anything inside it — ignore
# the specific unwanted subdirectory instead of the whole tree.
docs/superpowers/
.superpowers
.claude